---
// Small uppercase section label with the accent dash to its left.
// Usage: <Eyebrow>Install</Eyebrow>
---
<span style="position: relative; display: block; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); margin: 0 0 18px;">
  <span style="position: absolute; left: -64px; top: 6px; width: 44px; height: 1px; background: var(--color-accent);"></span>
  <slot />
</span>
